<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lovely-adj">lovely <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lʌvli/    美 /'lʌvli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>可爱的；美丽的；令人愉快的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a lovely baby 
可爱的婴儿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bride <strong>looked lovely</strong> in her wedding dress. 
新娘穿着婚纱看起来很漂亮。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We had a lovely holiday. 
我们度过了一个愉快的假期。</p></div></div>